# Cursor Rules for this repository

## Language and Communication
- Always write all comments, commit messages, and documentation in English
- Do not use Chinese characters in any code comments, commit messages, or documentation
- Translate any Chinese text to English when making changes

## Code Style
- Use clear, descriptive English comments
- Write commit messages in English following conventional commit format
- Maintain consistency with existing English documentation

## Repository Context
This is an OpenWRT CI project for cloud-based firmware compilation. All technical documentation and code should be in English for better international collaboration. 